Class Summary
Class Description
ConfirmedCases
Instances of ConfirmedCases contain required information for creating table and chart
table information : (total cases,total cases per million) for each country
chart information : (date,cumulative confirmed cases) for each country
ConfirmedCasesController
ConfirmedCasesController initializes ConfirmedCases scene
ConfirmedCasesRecord
Instances of ConfirmedCasesRecord contain totalCases and totalCasesPerMillion for a country
confirmedDeath
Instances of ConfirmedDeath contain required information for creating table and chart
table information : (total Death,total Death per million) for each country
chart information : (date,cumulative confirmed Death) for each country
ConfirmedDeathController
ConfirmedDeathController initializes ConfirmedDeath scene
confirmedDeathRecord
Instances of ConfirmedDeathRecord contain totalDeath and totalDeathPerMillion for a country
CountrySelection
Instances of CountrySelection represents a row in the countrySelectionTable.
CovidData
CovidData is an abstract class that contains user input : startDate,endDate,dataset,countries.

HomeController

LinearRegression

LinearRegressionController

MyApplication
The entry point of the entire program.
VaccinationRate

VaccinationRateRecord
